====================================================================================================
When given a prompt, classify the prompt based on the information above. Extract all available entities for a given ID as a JSON dictionary of lists. "examples" of entities are how a particular entity value is likely to appear. The JSON should be formatted as follows:

{ 
    "<intent1_id>": [ 
    {"slot_id": "<slot_id1>", "slot_value": "<slot_value1>"}, 
    {"slot_id": "<slot_id2>", "slot_value": "<slot_value2>"} 
] 
} 

If no entity is provided, return "none" for the associated slot ID and slot value.

Utterance: Hi there. I am checking on my visa application (ID 311FSA521) for my H1B. I will be relocating in less then 60 days and need to make sure that the visa has been approved. Can you provide me the status? I am the original applicant, it should be filed under the name James Durry.
